# RPG Server build & git

- **Stack:** Paper 26.1.2, Java 25, Maven shade → `target/rpg-server-*.jar`
- **Maven:** `C:\Users\Danie\tools\apache-maven-3.9.10\bin\mvn.cmd`
- **Civs JAR:** `../Civs-1.11.6/target/civs-1.11.6.jar` (build Civs first if missing)
- **Separate commits** per logical fix/feature; imperative message.
- Run **`mvn compile`** (or `mvn test` when tests exist) before push.
- Commit **`.cursor/skills/`** and **`.cursor/rules/`**; do not commit other `.cursor/` IDE state.
- Do **not** edit Civs source from this repo — integration via JAR + events only.
- Deploy JAR to server `plugins/`; user validates on Linux game server.
